---
const modules = [
  {
    title: "Meta Lead Generation",
    lessons: 6,
    duration: "2h",
    icon: "📱"
  },
  {
    title: "Google Ads Optimizacija",
    lessons: 5,
    duration: "1.5h",
    icon: "🔍"
  },
  {
    title: "CRM Avtomatizacija",
    lessons: 7,
    duration: "3h",
    icon: "🔗"
  },
  {
    title: "AI Reporting",
    lessons: 4,
    duration: "1h",
    icon: "📊"
  },
  {
    title: "AI Support Agenti",
    lessons: 6,
    duration: "2.5h",
    icon: "🤖"
  },
  {
    title: "Call Analytics",
    lessons: 4,
    duration: "1.5h",
    icon: "🎙️"
  }
];
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-dark-bg to-transparent">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-neon-purple to-neon-pink bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Learning Hub
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Študirajte na lastnem tempu z našimi strukturiranimi tečaji in mikro-vsebino.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      {modules.map((module) => (
        <div
          key={module.title}
          class="group relative p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#1a1f3a] border border-[#2d3561] hover:border-neon-purple/50 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer hover:translate-y-[-4px]"
        >
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">{module.icon}</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-neon-purple/20 text-neon-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Nov</span>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-neon-purple transition-colors">
            {module.title}
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <div>📚 {module.lessons} lekcij</div>
            <div>⏱️ {module.duration} naučnega časa</div>
          </div>

          <button class="w-full py-2 px-4 rounded-lg bg-neon-purple/20 text-neon-purple hover:bg-neon-purple/30 transition-colors font-semibold text-sm">
            Začni tečaj
          </button>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-neon-cyan/10 to-neon-purple/10 border border-[#2d3561] p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Niste sigurni, kje začeti?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Naš AI-vodnik vas bo vodil skozi personalizirane priporoče glede na vaše potrebe in cilje.
      </p>
      <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-neon-cyan to-neon-blue rounded-lg font-bold text-[#0a0e27] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-neon-cyan/50 transition-all">
        Najdi svoj tečaj
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
